@node "PACLAND"
PACLAND

When the title screen appears, type: "AVALON".  It should flash indicating
you now have unlimited lives!  If that doesn't work, try the following:

Start a 2 player game.  Make it as far as you can with player 1.  With player
2, you must be able to make it as far as the fairy to collect your boots.
Now that you have gotten your boots, you are going backwards to where you
started.  Push the 3'rd cactus on the way back, and a yellow pacman will
appear.  Get it, then kill player 2.  Continue playing with player 1.  Every
time player 1 dies, get the yellow pacman with player 2 and kill player 2
immediately.  As long as you keep getting the yellow pacman with player 2,
player 1 will never die.

Hints:

Level 1 - Run to the third fire hydrant, and when you get there, jump over it
          and push it to the left.  This will give you a blue hat that will
          make you invulnerable to the little ghosts that fall from planes.

Level 2 - Run to the third cactus, and push it to the left.  You will now be
          invulnerable for the entire level!

Level 3 - After getting your magic boots, push the third cactus on the way
          back for a free life.

- Jump on the roof of ghost's car to escape
- Only use powerpills when ghosts are in range, or else it is wasted
- When you reach the breaktime sign, jump when you are about 1 inch away
  for a bonus (depending how high you are when the level ends)
@endnode
@node "PANDORA"
PANDORA

  1: Wait a few moments for Amy to appear.
  2: Take ID Amy and find the Second Officer.  Pick up the Lazer Rifle
     from the table next to him.
  3: Put Lazer Rifle into backpack-don't use it yet.
  4: Find the Engineer, take his ID and the Sonic Driver.
  5: Find the Lt Commander, take his ID and carry it.
  6: Find the Commander, take his ID and carry it.  Also take the Code
     Blue and Code Scarlet.
  7: Find the Captain, take his SDI disk and leave the ID Lt. Commander.
  8: Shoot the Ice Lord with the Lazer Rifle.
  9: Carry the ID Engineer to go through the force field.
 10: Find the AWOL officer and take his ID.
 11: Carry the Sonic Driver and head for the Robomechanic.
 12: Swap the Sonic Driver for the Code Ochre.
 13: Carry the SDI Disk and go to the SDI computer.
 14: Give the SDI computer these items in the following order: SDI Disk,
     Code Scarlet, Code Ochre and Code Blue.
 15: Carry the Engineer's ID and exit the Engineering Section.  Then switch
     to ID AWOL.
 16: Go the transporter and enter along the arrow.
 17: That's all folks.
@endnode
@node "PANG"
PANG

On the map screen type "WHAT A NICE CHEAT".  The map should turn purple and
enable you to select any level to start on (be quick).
@endnode
@node "PANZA KICK BOXING"
PANZA KICK BOXING

The best moves to use are upper cut, round house, and low leg kick. The low
leg kick is useful for keeping your opponent out of range and on target for
a round house followed by an upper cut.  The double backfist is also very
powerful and often provides a knockout punch.  If you are losing a fight, and
don't have much chance of recovery, then press the 'ESC' key so that your
stats remain intact.
@endnode
@node "PARADROID"
PARADROID

On the title screen, hit 'F3' to bring up an options menu.
@endnode
@node "PARADROID 90"
PARADROID 90

On the title screen hit 'F3' to bring up an options menu.  The extra ship is
the Pirate Mothership.  To reach it, collect the Grafgold Key hidden on every
ship (The Grafgold Keys are usually found under crates and so on.  Collecting
a key keeps the Pirates at bay for a further three minutes.  A 5000 point
bonus is given for completing a ship with Grafgold key).  Complete the final
ship with every Grafgold Key to be beamed aboard the Pirate Mothership for a
fight to the death.
@endnode
@node "PARASOL STARS"
PARASOL STARS

Press the RIGHT MOUSE BUTTON to skip to the next level.

The cheat mode is activated by typing "CYNIX" during the game.  You can then
use the following keys:

 'M' - get all three stars                 'T' - end the stage
 'G' - kill all the badies on the screen   '1' - '7' - skip to that stage
 'C' - extra credit                        'F1' - 'F10' - skip to that level
 'D' - die                                 'B' - skip to bonus screen
 'X' - skip to extra level

Start a one-player game and plug in the mouse into player two's socket.  Then
press the right button to clear a level (Try using a Sega Genesis controller
with three buttons to play the game using this cheat method).
@endnode
@node "PAWN"
PAWN

After completing the game, once you have examined the listing type in
"DEBUG".  You will see the ">" prompt change to "]", and you will now be
invincible and able to wander anywhere in the game without being hurt.  Try
typing in "DEBUG" at the beginning of the game for the same effect.
@endnode
@node "PEGASUS"
PEGASUS

Level Passwords:

     1 - SCREECH
     2 - DRAGONFLY
     3 - BEEBOP
     4 - CELESTIAL
@endnode
@node "PENGO II"
PENGO II
    
Enter "CHEETAAH" for your password and use the 'HELP' key to skip levels.
Enter "ULTIMATE" to view the ending.
        
                                (LEVEL CODES)

            Level 0-"POSTCARD"  Level 3-"NEURONET"  Level 6-"GAUSSIAN"
            Level 1-"U2U2U2U2"  Level 4-"REPLOMAN"  Level 7-"BJORK4U2"
            Level 2-"SILENCIO"  Level 5-"RIVERGOD"  Level 8-"BULLROAR"
                                Level 9-"XENOCIDE"
@endnode
@node "PERSONAL NIGHTMARE"
PERSONAL NIGHTMARE

The safe can be opened by reading the date on the painting.
@endnode
@node "PETER BEARDSLEY'S INTERNATIONAL SOCCER"
PETER BEARDSLEY'S INTERNATIONAL SOCCER

Continual tapping of the fire button while in possession of the ball,
prevents any other players from tackling.
@endnode
@node "PGA TOUR GOLF"
PGA TOUR GOLF

Before you tee off on the first hole, click the button for the tournament
statistics.  Look through all of these and then play the game as usual and
you'll find that your opponents have dropped quite a few shots.  Do this on
each hole, and by the end of the game the computer players will be quite a
ways behind you.
@endnode
@node "PHANTASIA III"
PHANTASIA III

When you go to deposit some gold and are asked how much, type "9999999",
which then becomes a deposit of 27009.  Do not deposit any more or your
account will go back to nothing.
@endnode
@node "PHARAOHS CURSE"
PHARAOHS CURSE

Type "SPHINX" to start on level 2 or type "RAIDER" for level 3.
@endnode
@node "PHOTON STORM"
PHOTON STORM

Pause the game and type "YOUR-MIND-IS-MY-ASHTRAY" for invincibility (Where
the '-'s (minus signs) are on the main keyboard.
@endnode
@node "PINBALL FANTASIES"
PINBALL FANTASIES

Enter these cheats before you select the number of players.  After you've
loaded a pinball table and it scrolls up and down, you can enter these codes
(WITH spaces, no Return required):

    "FAIR PLAY"          -  Disables all previously entered cheats
    "EARTHQUAKE"         -  You may 'tilt' the table as you like
    "EXTRA BALLS"        -  Gives you 5 balls instead of 3
    "DIGITAL ILLUSIONS"  -  The ball cannot leave the table (You can only
                            leave the game by pressing: 'P' for pause and
                            'ESC' to quit the table).  Of course you won't be
                            able to enter your name on the high score table.
    "VACUUM CLEANER"     -  Clears the highscore list
    "HIGHLANDER"         -  Makes your ball heavier
@endnode
@node "PINBALL MAGIC"
PINBALL MAGIC

When the exit to the next level opens, you can press 'F4' to go to the next
level.
@endnode
@node "PIPELINE"
PIPELINE

Here are the codes:  FOLD,  EYES,  EGGS,  TEAR,  PEAS,  DUCT, and  PODS
@endnode
@node "PIPEMANIA"
PIPEMANIA

Here are some passwords:

  4: GRIP, 8: TICK, 12: DUCK, 16: OOZE, 20: BLOB, 24: BALL, 28: WILD.

For a 4000 point bonus, you need to get the flooze to cross itself FIVE
times.  But remember not to get too cocky, and wait until the end of the pipe
to do this.  There is also a secret bonus of 50,000 points if you completely
fill the screen with pipes.
@endnode
@node "PIRATES"
PIRATES

When fighting against unbelievable odds dont panic.  Choose the long-sword.
Keep using the slash-high attack to cause the most dammage.  You may get down
to only one man left, but you can still defeat the enemy captain.  After you
win, select "Send A Prize Crew", so you will have enough people to sail your
ship.  Don't attack a nation that your home country is allied with as it will
upset both of them.  Your oppurtunities will be much better if you don't wed
untill you've got all your promotions.  Engage in conversation with all the
Governor's daughters as may gather important information for you from the
Governors mansion.
@endnode
@node "PIT-FIGHTER (Domark)"
PIT-FIGHTER


To skip levels, simply type in the word "LOBSTERS" while a fight is in
progress and press either '1', '2', or '3', for the respective levels.  Then
try these keys:

 'C' - For the final championship round. 
 'G' - For a grudge match.
 'L' - For an elimination round.
@endnode
@node "PLAGUE"
PLAGUE

First make your score end in a three (by shooting the bubbles).  Then hit "P"
to pause the game.  Hit 'Escape' and then click on "No" when asked if you
want to play again.  Dong so takes you to the title screen with the drooling
barbarian.  Now type the following: "KOM JE ILLEGAAL DOOR DE PLAAG DAN GRIJPT
DE JUNGLE COMMAND JE IN DE KRAGG" followed by 'Return'.  The border should
have become green.  Hit the fire button to return to the game.  You now have
infinite lives.  You must do this on Level 1 before being killed even once.
@endnode
@node "PLATOON"
PLATOON

This one's cute.  Type in "Hamburger" at the title screen.  The word "Cheat"
will appear below the credits.  Press your joystck button, then 'F5' when the
jungle screen comes up.  Your man is now invulnerable to the attacks of the
little Commie @#!!$&+s.  From here 'F1' starts you where you are, 'F2' puts
you at the location of the explosives, 'F3' takes you to the bridges that you
have to blow up, 'F4' takes you straight to the village where the entrance to
the tunnels is hidden in one of the huts.  From here on the cheat no longer
works, the game runs as normal and you can die but it certainly gets you
further along the track.

Type "HAMBURGER - HILL" (include hyphen and spaces) on the title screen.  You
can now get to the TNT by pressing 'F2', the bridge with 'F3' and the village
with 'F4' and 'F5' to gain immunity from everything.
@endnode
@node "PLAYER MANAGER"
PLAYER MANAGER

1) Buy a few young, cheap players and keep them in the squad for a whole
season.  Next year, their price will have increased and you should have no
trouble selling them for a huge profit.
2) Only buy players with very high agility ratings, as this effects all
their other attributes.  If agility is high (about 200), expect the player
to become an excellent footballer, given a season or two.
4) Remove 8 or 9 players from your team, then after 2 or 3 big defeats, you
will receive sponsorship.
@endnode
@node "POD (PD)"
POD (PD)

On the title screen, type "BIGCOUNTRY" and then a level number.  Example:
Type "BIGCOUNTRY45", then press 'F1' (1 player) or 'F2' (2 players).  You
will start on level 45.
@endnode
@node "POING (PD)"
POING (PD)

On the title screen, hold the 'LEFT SHIFT' key and press '[' to enter the
editor.  Also press 'R-AMIGA' and 'N' to go to workbench and 'R-AMIGA' and
'M' to get back to the game.
@endnode
@node "POOL OF RADIANCE"
POOL OF RADIANCE

Once you find any item you can make as many copies of it as you want.
     1 - Create a dummy character.
     2 - Load a saved game and transfer all the good items to the dummy.
     3 - Remove the dummy character from the party.
     4 - Load the dummy character back in.
     5 - Transfer the items to other members.
     6 - Drop the dummy character from the party.
     7 - Repeat steps 4-6 as many times as needed.
     This also works for Curse of the Azure Bonds and Champions of Krynn.
@endnode
@node "POPEYE 2"
POPEYE 2

    Level Codes:  Level 2 - SUBURBAN
                  Level 3 - SOOTY
                  Level 4 - DUCKULA
@endnode
