When you bring up the options screen in a Conquest game, you can enter a
number from 0 to 32768; the program will generate a world associated with
whatever number you type in.  This gives you 128,000 worlds to choose from!!!
If you enter "KILLUSPAL", it will put you on world 999.  Hmm...
@endnode
@node "POPULUS II"
POPULUS II

When the "Choose your Deity" screen appeass, enter "ADKIUCMCZNDIFINL" to
start the game with maximum power gor in all areas of godly control.  Note
Amiga Action gives the password as "ADKITAKDVGZLRGWZ".

To activate lightning, hold down the Left Mouse Button, Press '1' on the
keyboard, and release the Mouse Button.  Now the lightning remains and your
manna won't decrease.  Amazing!

