@node "POWER, THE"
POWER, THE

Hold down any of the following key combinations during play:

 'CTRL' and 'B'               - Causes the background scrolling to stop.
 'L SHIFT', 'R SHIFT' and 'T' - Causes time to stop.
 'L ALT', 'R ALT' and 'H'     - Causes aAll hearts to be collected.
 'L AMIGA', 'R AMIGA' and 'S' - Skip levels.

Level codes:

   Level  Code       Level  Code       Level  Code       Level  Code
   ------------      ------------      ------------      ------------
     2 - LEVEL2        3 - VISUAL        4 - COWBOY        5 - URGENT
     6 - OOPSUP        7 - TOPTEN        8 - D14DH7        9 - ASDFGH
    10 - SOLONG       11 - SURFIN       12 - RACKET       13 - BULLIT
    14 - QRAZZY       15 - 36F6FR       16 - UNLINK       17 - PIXXEL
    18 - EUROPE       19 - NEWTON       20 - FREEZE       21 - LAUNCH
    22 - M7MS49       23 - GALVAN       24 - KLOWWM       25 - INDIGO
