PUTTY

On the high score screen after the games is over (you don't need a high
score), type "HEADLIKEAHOLE" and press the 'ENTER' key on the numeric keypad.
Use 'F1-F10' to skip levels.  This also gives you infinite lives.
@endnode        
@node "PUZZNIC"
PUZZNIC

When playing the game, press the space bar to bring up the retry screen, but
don't release the spacebar. All the time that it is held down the game will
be paused and you can work out what to do without having to rush.

